{"id":945,"parent_id":942,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":945,"title":"Zephaniah 3","subtitle":"","short_title":"Zeph.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 3"],[".studySummary",["i","At the Second Coming, all nations will assemble to battle—Men will have a pure language—The Lord will reign in their midst."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.1","order":"02.37.003.62553"},["b","1"],"Woe to her that is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"filthy"],"and polluted, to the oppressing city!"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.2","order":"02.37.003.62554"},["b","2"],"She",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"obeyed not"],"the voice; she received not correction; she trusted not in the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; she drew not near to her God."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.3","order":"02.37.003.62555"},["b","3"],"Her princes within her",["i","are"],"roaring lions; her judges",["i","are"],"evening",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"wolves"],"; they gnaw not the bones till the morrow."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.4","order":"02.37.003.62556"},["b","4"],"Her prophets",["i","are"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"light"],["i","and"],"treacherous persons: her priests have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"polluted"],"the sanctuary, they have done violence to the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"law"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.5","order":"02.37.003.62557"},["b","5"],"The just",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","is"],"in the midst thereof; he will not do iniquity: every morning doth he bring his judgment to light, he faileth not; but the unjust knoweth no shame."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.6","order":"02.37.003.62558"},["b","6"],"I have cut off the nations: their towers are desolate; I made their streets waste, that none passeth by: their cities are destroyed, so that there is no man, that there is none inhabitant."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.7","order":"02.37.003.62559"},["b","7"],"I said, Surely thou wilt fear me, thou wilt receive instruction; so their dwelling should not be cut off, howsoever I punished them: but they rose early,",["i","and"],"corrupted all their doings."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.8","order":"02.37.003.62560"},["b","8"],"¶Therefore wait ye upon me, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", until the day that I rise up to the prey: for my determination",["i","is"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"to"],"gather the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"nations"],", that I may assemble the kingdoms, to pour upon them mine indignation,",["i","even"],"all my fierce anger: for all the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"earth"],"shall be devoured with the fire of my jealousy."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.9","order":"02.37.003.62561"},["b","9"],"For then will I turn to the people a pure",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"language"],", that they may all call upon the name of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", to serve him with one",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"consent"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.10","order":"02.37.003.62562"},["b","10"],"From",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"beyond"],"the rivers of Ethiopia my suppliants,",["i","even"],"the daughter of my dispersed, shall bring mine offering."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.11","order":"02.37.003.62563"},["b","11"],"In that day shalt thou not be ashamed for all thy doings, wherein thou hast transgressed against me: for then I will take away out of the midst of thee them that rejoice in thy pride, and thou shalt no more be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"haughty"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"because of"],"my holy mountain."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.12","order":"02.37.003.62564"},["b","12"],"I will also leave in the midst of thee an afflicted and poor people, and they shall trust in the name of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.13","order":"02.37.003.62565"},["b","13"],"The remnant of Israel shall not do iniquity, nor speak",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"lies"],"; neither shall a deceitful tongue be found in their mouth: for they shall feed and lie down, and none shall make",["i","them"],"afraid."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.14","order":"02.37.003.62566"},["b","14"],"¶Sing, O daughter of Zion; shout, O Israel; be glad and rejoice with all the heart, O daughter of Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.15","order":"02.37.003.62567"},["b","15"],"The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath taken away thy judgments, he hath cast out thine enemy: the king of Israel,",["i","even"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["i","is"],"in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"midst"],"of thee: thou shalt not see evil any more."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.16","order":"02.37.003.62568"},["b","16"],"In that day it shall be said to Jerusalem, Fear thou not:",["i","and to"],"Zion, Let not thine hands be slack."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.17","order":"02.37.003.62569"},["b","17"],"The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God in the midst of thee",["i","is"],"mighty; he will save, he will rejoice over thee with joy; he will rest in his love, he will joy over thee with singing."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.18","order":"02.37.003.62570"},["b","18"],"I will gather",["i","them that are"],"sorrowful for the solemn assembly,",["i","who"],"are of thee,",["i","to whom"],"the reproach of it",["i","was"],"a burden."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.19","order":"02.37.003.62571"},["b","19"],"Behold, at that time I will undo all that afflict thee: and I will save her that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"halteth"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"gather"],"her that was driven out; and I will get them praise and fame in every land where they have been put to shame."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.20","order":"02.37.003.62572"},["b","20"],"At that time will I bring you",["i","again,"],"even in the time that I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"gather"],"you: for I will make you a name and a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"praise"],"among all people of the earth, when I turn back your",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"captivity"],"before your eyes, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.1a","order":"02.37.003.62573"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/filthiness"},"TG Filthiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.2a","order":"02.37.003.62575"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/disobedience"},"TG Disobedience"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.3a","order":"02.37.003.62577"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.6"},"Jer. 5:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.4a","order":"02.37.003.62579"},["b","4a"],["span.small","OR"],"wanton."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.4b","order":"02.37.003.62581"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sacrilege"},"TG Sacrilege"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.4c","order":"02.37.003.62583"},["b","4c"],["span.small","HEB"],["span.translit",["span.emphasis","torah."]]],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.8a","order":"02.37.003.62585"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.2.1-2"},"Joel 3:2 (1–2)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.8b","order":"02.37.003.62587"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/13.4"},"Isa. 13:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.8c","order":"02.37.003.62589"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-destiny-of"},"TG Earth, Destiny of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/world-end-of"},"World, End of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.9a","order":"02.37.003.62591"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/communication"},"TG Communication"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/language"},"Language"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.9b","order":"02.37.003.62593"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/common-consent"},"TG Common Consent"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/unity"},"Unity"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.10a","order":"02.37.003.62595"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/18.1"},"Isa. 18:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.11a","order":"02.37.003.62597"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/haughtiness"},"TG Haughtiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.11b","order":"02.37.003.62599"},["b","11b"],["span.small","HEB"],"in."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.13a","order":"02.37.003.62601"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/lying"},"TG Lying"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.15a","order":"02.37.003.62603"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-millennial-reign"},"TG Jesus Christ, Millennial Reign"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.19a","order":"02.37.003.62605"},["b","19a"],["span.small","OR"],"is lame."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.19b","order":"02.37.003.62607"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-gathering-of"},"TG Israel, Gathering of"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.20a","order":"02.37.003.62609"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.4"},"Isa. 63:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.20b","order":"02.37.003.62611"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/62.7"},"Isa. 62:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"20c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.20c","order":"02.37.003.62613"},["b","20c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/30.3.1-5"},"Deut. 30:3 (1–5)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/2.7"},"Zeph. 2:7"],"."]]}
